<speak>
  Hello{{#if callerName}}, {{callerName}}{{/if}}.
  {{pause 300}}
  This is an automated message from your service provider.

  {{#ifGt missedPayments 0}}
    Our records show that your account ending in {{spellDigits accountNumber}}
    has {{missedPayments}} missed payment{{#ifGt missedPayments 1}}s{{/ifGt}}.
    Your current balance is {{speakCurrency balance}}, due on {{dueDate}}.
    {{pause 400}}
    To make a payment now, please press 1.
    To speak with a representative, press 2.
  {{else}}
    {{#if isPremiumMember}}
      As a valued {{pick isPremiumMember "Premium" "Standard"}} member,
      your account ending in {{spellDigits accountNumber}} is in good standing.
    {{else}}
      Your account ending in {{spellDigits accountNumber}} is in good standing.
    {{/if}}
    {{pause 300}}
    Your next payment of {{speakCurrency balance}} is due on {{dueDate}}.
  {{/ifGt}}

  {{pause 500}}
  If you have questions, please call us at {{speakPhone callbackNumber}}.

  Thank you for being a {{pick isPremiumMember "Premium" "valued"}} customer.
  Goodbye.
</speak>
